[msg MSG_020_0_0 [Taxista]]
[f 2 1][f 5 21 1 416]Aah... Uh... Eh...[n][w][e]
[f 2 1][f 5 21 1 416]Ah... Ah...Ahhh...[n][w][e]

[msg MSG_021_0_0 [Taxista]]
